SUMMARY:Interchange Message: WALTHAMSTOW CENTRAL STATION: Until January 
 2026\, there will be no lift service from street level (Bus station) to 
 ticket hall. This is while planned maintenance works takes place. If you 
 have luggage\, buggies or difficulties using stairs\, please use the exit 
 via the London Overground ticket hall to Selborne\nRoad. There are fewer 
 steps and a ramp between the ticket hall and the street. There is a 
 pedestrian crossing to the bus station from the station exit. For access 
 to the Victoria line avoiding stairs - use bus route 230 from stop M on 
 Selborne Walk / Selborne Road to Tottenham Hale station.
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR